  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626232/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201407/fa2fa6bfc76243929188663f59be9188.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThe 298 passengers and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/crew\" target=\"_blank\">crew</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/aboard\" target=\"_blank\">aboard</a> MH17 will have been <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/oblivious\" target=\"_blank\">oblivious</a> to the horror as a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/shrapnel\" target=\"_blank\">shrapnel</a>-based <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/missile\" target=\"_blank\">missile</a> instantly <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/shred\" target=\"_blank\">shredded</a> the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/doomed\" target=\"_blank\">doomed</a> plane, experts claim.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">有专家表示，载有298人的马航MH17是在毫不知情的情况下遭受到榴霰弹的袭击，导致机体瞬间粉碎。</span></p>\n<p>\n\tThe SA-11 missile - known as a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Grizzly\" target=\"_blank\">Grizzly</a> - that hit the doomed <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Malaysian\" target=\"_blank\">Malaysian</a> Airlines flight is designed to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/pulverise\" target=\"_blank\">pulverise</a> aircraft on <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/impact\" target=\"_blank\">impact</a>.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">击中马航客机的元凶是型号为SA-11的导弹（俗称&ldquo;灰熊&rdquo;），它令遇难客机在受到冲击时瓦解。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201407/408dedf75091402f8f6bf25acea1c1e6.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tIt will have <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/perforat\" target=\"_blank\">perforated</a> the plane at various points, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/ignite\" target=\"_blank\">ignited</a> the fuel, and taken out the engines and the wings within a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/split second\" target=\"_blank\">split second</a> - meaning the people aboard will have been unconscious almost instantly.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">导弹在机体上贯穿出很多孔，点燃了燃料，紧接着就摧毁了引擎和机翼&mdash;&mdash;这意味着当时机上的乘客还不明白到底发生了什么。</span></p>\n<p>\n\tThe surface-to-air missile hit the Boeing 777 with such force that residents in the area claim to have seen bodies falling from the sky &lsquo;like rags&rsquo;.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">有当地居民目击了地对空导弹击中这架波音777客机的情形&mdash;&mdash;分解的机体从天上落下，就像&ldquo;破布&rdquo;一样。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201407/fa0936f44e324494b7d365709c86c4bb.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tJustin Bronk, researcher analyst at the Royal United Services Institute (RUSI), told MailOnline: 'An SA-11 missile is designed to shred aircraft.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">皇家国防联合研究所的调查分析员</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">贾斯汀&middot;布郎克告诉每日邮报：&ldquo;设计SA-11导弹的目的就是为了摧毁飞行器。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t'The missile is programmed using a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/tracker\" target=\"_blank\">tracker</a> to get within a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/metre\" target=\"_blank\">metre</a> of the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/target\" target=\"_blank\">target</a> then let off a ring of shrapnel, which will enter the aircraft at various points.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&quot;这种导弹带有一个追踪器，它能在距目标一米之内释放环形的弹片，在机身上击穿无数个孔。&quot;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t'The shrapnel will have hit the wings, the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/engine\" target=\"_blank\">engines</a> and the fuel tanks, igniting the fuel.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;弹片击中机翼、引擎和油箱，点燃了燃料。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t'A large aircraft like that is highly <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/pressurise\" target=\"_blank\">pressurised</a> to allow humans to breathe at that <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/altitude\" target=\"_blank\">altitude</a> so it will have exploded instantly.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;大型飞机通常处于高压状态，以使乘客能在高空呼吸，也因此它在短时间内就会爆炸。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t'Almost nobody on board would have known what was happening. If not instantly, they will have been <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unconscious\" target=\"_blank\">unconscious</a> within split seconds.'<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;机上的人几乎都没有意识到发生了什么。即使不是立即发生的，他们也会在极短的时间内失去知觉。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626232/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626232\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p625802/\">经典美剧来袭，这样学口语最有效！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626118/\">两次马航：妻子调班逃生，丈夫调班丧命</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626050/\">马航客机被击落 295人恐全部丧生</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626157/\">万恶风俗 非洲妇女15孩被喂鳄鱼</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626088/\">乌克兰民间武装承认误击马航客机</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p625956/\">被拐16年后成选美冠军 少女终与家人团聚</a></li><li